{"tid":2370882,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中環碼頭有間高質良心蟹堡冇人講！！！","createTime":"2021-01-18T10:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T11:46:48.000Z","uid":305072,"like":19,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a35adab2747495dbdbf934127d7763a4feb52ec2","tid":2370882,"uid":305072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjVD3aK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjVD3aK.jpg&h=1a0e0681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCrab Cake, 係用麵包糠炸嘅，唔係煎的。有滿滿嘅蟹肉，非常鮮甜，食完簡直想問下有冇得單叫Crab Cake，真係好好好食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6hKYJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6hKYJ4.jpg&h=025b26da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牛肉係用USDA Prime Grade，所以好重牛味，仲勁爆Juicy，大家唔好一下太大力咬落去，一大力咬，啲肉汁噴到全身都係，真係「瀨尿牛丸丫笨」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1oi2Lo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1oi2Lo3.jpg&h=830747f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左Burger仲有薯條同手工啤，一樣咁高質<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hQENb35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhQENb35.jpg&h=1d5b4c79&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smUtFXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsmUtFXp.jpg&h=96329112&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n明明哩間Burger鋪咁高質但發現好多人都唔知，仲要間鋪有貼文宣，.gun<br />\n<br />\nGot Beef<br />\n地址：中環七號碼頭上層F舖<br />\n<br />\n依家鋪頭仲有同Treviu合作，輕鬆寫篇食評又賺$10 Burger Coupon<br />\n<a href=\"https://treviu.com/burger-10-off\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftreviu.com%2Fburger-10-off&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS8ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=96769bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://treviu.com/burger-10-off</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：我哋係Treviu團隊，宗旨係提供真食評，唔會因為讚定彈而過濾你嘅食評<br />\n<br />\n如果想睇更多真食評嘅話可以支持下我哋：<br />\niOS/Android: <a href=\"http://onelink.to/vvvqnq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonelink.to%